Rubik 3D game is the Rubik Cube game ported to your desktop using
Clutter and Vala. This program is released under the terms of the
GNU General Public License, see the file `COPYING' for more information.

Type `make' to compile then `./rubik' to start playing.

USAGE
- To rotate a cube slice click on a face and move the mouse.
- To rotate the view either right click, click outside
  the cube or keep SHIFT pressed.
- To rotate the cube around itself press either `a', `q', `w', `e', `d'
  or `s'
